值得关注，绝不是像郭智辉所说的那样对台积电影响不大。《中国时报》此前刊登的一篇评论称，台积电赴美设厂，岛内一方面担忧台积电此举是否会造成关键技术外流，另一方面则担心中美芯片战持续拉锯。评论认为，台积电正在“去台化”，虽然芯片厂商还是设立在台湾，但所做的许多决定已非台湾所能左右。（陈立非）4纳米芯片在美量产，台媒：台积电正“去台化”，许多决定已非台湾所能左右"},"attached_info":"CkAIqrnohp72updvEAMaCTExMjg2OTUzOCDUj5K8BjAAODtAFHIKOTQ2NTU5MjAwNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"30 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-00c58c76225ad932f37a4cd5fa20f2c6_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1736771330.81856","card_id":"Q_9473986277","target":{"id":9473986277,"title":"中国人民解放军东部战区代表团将于 1 月中旬访问日本，有哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/9473986277","type":"question","created":1736746701,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":97,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[229,1234,2161,18963,31772],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"经双方商定，中国人民解放军东部战区代表团将于1月中旬访问日本。期间，代表团将会见日本防卫省、自卫队联合参谋部领导，参访有关军事单位。此访有助于增进双方理解互信，促进中日防务交流。中国人民解放军东部战区代表团将访问日本-国际在线"},"attached_info":"CkAIqrnohp72updvEAMaCTExMjg3MTIyOCDNzZK8BjAAOGFAFXIKOTQ3Mzk4NjI3N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"30 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ec3f8aa86219f6f2b962c1d98e05c045_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1736771330.82234","card_id":"Q_7729626185","target":{"id":7729626185,"title":"为什么健身时「核心收紧」要刻意强调出来？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/7729626185","type":"question","created":1735026637,"answer_count":25,"follower_count":109,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[658,57283],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIqrnohp72updvEAMaCTExMjUyMjQyOCDNz6m7BjAAOG1AFnIKNzcyOTYyNjE4NXgAqgEJ